 action ''')''' constReturns {{Span|true}} if the given event is part of an existing action. This method ignores keyboard modifiers if the given [[InputEvent GD|InputEvent]] is not pressed (for proper release detection). See [[#action_has_event|action_has_event]] if you don't want this behavior.=== get_action_list ===*  [[Array GD|Array]] '''get_action_list''' '''(''' [[StringName GD|StringName]] action ''')'''Returns an array of [[InputEvent GD|InputEvent]]\ s associated with a given action.=== get_actions ===*  [[Array GD|Array]] '''get_actions ( )'''Returns an array of all actions in the {{Span|InputMap}}.=== has_action ===*  bool '''has_action''' '''(''' [[StringName GD|StringName]] action ''')''' constReturns {{Span|true}} if the {{Span|InputMap}} has a registered action with the given name.=== load_from_globals ===*  void '''load_from_globals ( )'''Clears all [[InputEventAction GD|InputEventAction]] in the {{Span|InputMap}} and load it anew from [[ProjectSettings GD|ProjectSettings]].